{
  "title": "Slow Smoky Clay Pot Japanese Chicken Tagine",
  "description": "A rich and flavorful one-pot dish featuring chicken thighs, sweet potatoes, and Japanese spices, all slow-cooked to perfection in a clay tajine.",
  "cuisine": "Japanese",
  "diet": [
