  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300°F (150°C).",
    "Season the chicken thighs with salt and pepper.",
    "Heat the coconut oil in the clay tajine over medium heat. Add the chicken thighs and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the diced sweet potatoes, white miso paste, grated ginger, brown sugar, soy sauce, and water to the tajine.",
    "Stir to combine, then cover the tajine and transfer it to the preheated oven.",
    "Bake for 45 minutes, or until the chicken is cooked through and the sweet potatoes are tender.",
    "Remove the tajine from the oven and stir in the chopped green onions and toasted sesame seeds.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional green onions and sesame seeds if desired.",
    "Let the dish rest for 10 minutes before serving."
  ],
